Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 56th Weekly Dose of Optimism.
Another big week of Optimism over here at Not Boring HQ. We filled all of t=
he slots for this week=E2=80=99s edition by mid-evening on Wednesday, which=
 is about 36 hours ahead of our usual schedule. All that optimism makes our=
 jobs a bit easier and the world a bit better.
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
The Weekly Dose is brought to you by=E2=80=A6Ramp [ https://link.sbstck.com=
/redirect/8705da69-23a4-466e-9eb0-fc50f0c9743f?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5=
T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
